<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Staff21x - Trabajadores Digitales</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;600;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #7B68EE;
            --primary-dark: #5D3FD3;
            --accent: #9D7FFF;
            --dark: #0F0F1A;
            --dark-gray: #1A1A2E;
            --light-gray: #E8E8F0;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --success: #00D9A3;
            --gold: #FFA500;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background: var(--dark);
            color: var(--white);
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Fondos animados */
        .animated-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .gradient-bg {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 50%, var(--dark) 100%);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientShift 15s ease infinite;
        }

        .grid-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            animation: gridMove 20s linear infinite;
        }

        .lines-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(
                    0deg,
                    transparent,
                    transparent 2px,
                    rgba(157, 127, 255, 0.03) 2px,
                    rgba(157, 127, 255, 0.03) 4px
                );
            animation: linesMove 10s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes gradientShift {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        @keyframes gridMove {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
            100% { transform: translate(50px, 50px); }
        }

        @keyframes linesMove {
            0% { transform: translateY(0); }
            100% { transform: translateY(4px); }
        }

        .slides-container {
            height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
        }

        .slide {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(100%);
            transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 4rem;
        }

        .slide.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .slide.prev {
            transform: translateX(-100%);
        }

        .slide-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1400px;
        }

        /* Logo AJUSTADO */
        .logo {
            position: fixed;
            top: 2.5rem;
            left: 2.5rem;
            z-index: 100;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 45px; /* Reducido de 90px a 45px */
            width: auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 16px rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.5));
        }

        /* Navegación */
        .nav-controls {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 3rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            z-index: 100;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.5s both;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            background: rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            color: var(--white);
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.6);
        }

        .nav-btn:disabled {
            opacity: 0.3;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }

        .nav-btn:disabled:hover {
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: none;
            background: rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.2);
        }

        .slide-indicator {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 3rem;
            right: 3rem;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            z-index: 100;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.7s both;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInRight {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes scaleIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        .animate-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        }

        /* Slide 1 - Portada */
        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .hero-title .highlight {
            color: var(--primary);
            display: block;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
            color: var(--accent);
            text-align: left;
        }

        /* Títulos generales */
        .slide-title {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .accent-bar {
            width: 150px;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--gold));
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.5);
        }

        /* Slide 2 - VENTAJA COMPETITIVA */
        .advantage-cards {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .advantage-card {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            opacity: 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .advantage-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent, rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.05));
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .advantage-card h3 {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .advantage-card h3 .icon {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .advantage-card p {
            color: var(--light-gray);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* Slide 3 - Analogía */
        .analogy-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .steps-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .step-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 2px solid rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.3);
        }

        .step-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .step-content p {
            color: var(--light-gray);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary));
            padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.4);
        }

        /* Slide 4 - Casos de Uso */
        .use-cases-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .use-cases-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }

        .use-case {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8);
            padding: 1.2rem;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--success);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .use-case h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .use-case p {
            color: var(--light-gray);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .question-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary));
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.4);
        }

        .question-box h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .question-box p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--light-gray);
        }

        .question-box .highlight {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Video container */
        .video-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
        }

        .video-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 177.78%;
            height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 2px solid rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.3);
        }

        .video-wrapper iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }

        .video-caption {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--light-gray);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* Proceso */
        .process-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .process-step {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        .process-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .checklist {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .checklist li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .checklist li::before {
            content: "✓";
            color: var(--success);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .two-columns {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .column-card {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .column-card h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .column-card ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .column-card li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            color: var(--light-gray);
        }

        .column-card li::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .highlight-text {
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .time-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--success);
            color: var(--dark);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .tools-grid {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .tool {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .tool-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(15, 15, 26, 0.8);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .tool-name {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--light-gray);
        }

        .info-box {
            background: rgba(15, 15, 26, 0.8);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--success);
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .info-box p {
            color: var(--light-gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .rocket-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary));
            padding: 2rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.4);
        }

        .rocket-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        /* Diferenciadores */
        .diff-cards {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .diff-card {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .diff-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .diff-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .diff-content p {
            color: var(--light-gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Próximos Pasos */
        .investment-section {
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .investment-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .investment-box {
            background: rgba(15, 15, 26, 0.8);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .investment-box h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .investment-box ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .investment-box li {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            color: var(--light-gray);
        }

        .investment-box li::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .investment-note {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .investment-note span {
            color: var(--light-gray);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* Cierre */
        .final-message {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .final-message .line-1 {
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .final-message .line-2 {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .final-message .line-3 {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .contact-box {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8);
            padding: 2rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .contact-brand {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-info {
            color: var(--light-gray);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .slide {
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .logo img {
                height: 35px; /* Reducido de 60px a 35px para versión móvil */
            }

            .use-cases-grid,
            .two-columns {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .nav-controls {
                bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .slide-indicator {
                bottom: 2rem;
                right: 2rem;
            }

            .video-wrapper {
                padding-bottom: 56.25%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Staff21x">
    </div>

    <div class="slide-indicator">
        <span id="current-slide">1</span> / 11
    </div>

    <div class="nav-controls">
        <button class="nav-btn" id="prev-btn" disabled>←</button>
        <button class="nav-btn" id="next-btn">→</button>
    </div>

    <div class="slides-container" id="slides-container">
        
        <div class="slide active" data-slide="1">
            <div class="animated-bg">
                <div class="gradient-bg"></div>
                <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
                <div class="lines-overlay"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="slide-content">
                <h1 class="hero-title animate-in">
                    TRABAJADORES
                    <span class="highlight">DIGITALES</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle animate-in" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                    Contratá talento sin límites físicos ni cargas sociales
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="slide" data-slide="2">
            <div class="animated-bg">
                <div class="gradient-bg"></div>
                <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
                <div class="lines-overlay"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="slide-content">
                <h2 class="slide-title">LA VENTAJA COMPETITIVA</h2>
                <div class="accent-bar"></div>
                <div class="advantage-cards">
                    <div class="advantage-card">
                        <h3><span class="icon">🚀</span> Adelantate al mercado</h3>
                        <p>Mientras tu competencia sigue buscando talento humano para escalar, vos ya estás operando 24/7 sin límites de capacidad.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="advantage-card">
                        <h3><span class="icon">💰</span> ROI inmediato</h3>
                        <p>Eliminás cargas sociales (60-80%), tiempos de contratación (45-90 días), y rotación constante. La inversión se recupera en el primer mes.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="advantage-card">
                        <h3><span class="icon">⚡</span> Velocidad de implementación</h3>
                        <p>De la decisión a operación productiva en 7-10 días. Mientras otros esperan meses por un candidato, vos ya estás generando ingresos.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="advantage-card">
                        <h3><span class="icon">🎯</span> Early adopter advantage</h3>
                        <p>Los que adoptan ahora, lideran mañana. Cuando esto sea commodity, vos ya vas a tener 2 años de ventaja operativa y aprendizaje.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="slide" data-slide="3">
            <div class="animated-bg">
                <div class="gradient-bg"></div>
                <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
                <div class="lines-overlay"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="slide-content">
                <h2 class="slide-title">¿CÓMO CONTRATARÍAS UNA PERSONA?</h2>
                <p class="analogy-subtitle">Así funcionamos nosotros. Exactamente igual.</p>
                
                <div class="steps-container">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">📋</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3>1. Job Description</h3>
                            <p>Definís qué hace y qué no hace</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">👥</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3>2. Entrevistas</h3>
                            <p>Seleccionás el perfil adecuado</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">🛠️</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3>3. Herramientas</h3>
                            <p>Le das correo, WhatsApp, notebook</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">🧠</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3>4. Capacitación</h3>
                            <p>Le explicás cómo funciona TU empresa</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
